                    "body": "`arrow.ipc.RecordBatchReader._import_from_c` (this may be the issue); I also tried RecordBatchStreamReader.\r\n\r\nFor reference the code is I am using is here: https://github.com/jorgecarleitao/arrow2/pull/857, this line: https://github.com/jorgecarleitao/arrow2/pull/857/files#diff-721d8214320dcf310ab55f0de12a4ed43e910df50f959b8c0660ef1a73aa7950R51\r\n\r\nI am getting this by passing an empty iterator (i.e. one where the returned array has always been released.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
