                        "timeZone": "Europe/Paris"
                    },
                    "body": "bq. Other than that, the only thing I was unable to find was an API in Python to write arrays other than StructArray / RecordBatch\r\n\r\nYes, because basically this wraps the C++ APIs which only know about RecordBatchReader. Is it important for you to write/read any kind of array?\r\n",
